entry.name: HAProxy_2_4
entry.description: Monitors HAProxy stats for v2.4. Needs graph definitions.
entry.technology:
Tested to work with HAProxy 2.4 and with this sample config: frontend stats bind :8404 mode http log global maxconn 10
timeout client 100s timeout server 100s timeout connect 100s timeout queue 100s
stats enable stats hide-version stats refresh 30s stats show-node stats uri /haproxy?stats
frontend mysite frontend hissite frontend theothersite frontend google.com
